He is having something
of an existential crisis.

36:21.780 --> 36:23.715
Pay him no mind.

36:23.749 --> 36:26.385
But seriously,
do you have a plan?

36:26.418 --> 36:27.953
Yes.

36:28.186 --> 36:30.289
Separate the king
from Mary's influence.

36:30.322 --> 36:32.424
He worships her,
if you hadn't noticed.

36:32.457 --> 36:35.627
And that is why the separation
must be made by force.

36:35.661 --> 36:37.496
Some time alone
with his Protestant uncles

36:37.529 --> 36:41.366
to remind him of the benefits
of religious tolerance.

36:41.400 --> 36:43.902
Sounds quite practical.

36:43.936 --> 36:45.203
<i>Thank you, Antoine.</i>

36:45.237 --> 36:46.538
You are, if I'm not mistaken,

36:46.572 --> 36:48.607
talking about
kidnapping the king.

36:48.640 --> 36:51.276
There is nothing
remotely practical about it.

36:51.310 --> 36:53.845
Yeah. If the Guises find out,
they will declare war.

36:53.879 --> 36:55.581
<i>The Guises will not find out.</i>

36:56.248 --> 36:57.316
The king will be seized

36:57.349 --> 36:59.952
by unknown
Protestant militants.

36:59.985 --> 37:01.920
You will negotiate his release,

37:01.954 --> 37:03.422
<i>kill the militants,</i>

37:03.455 --> 37:06.792
and return him unharmed
as an act of patriotism,

37:06.825 --> 37:09.561
and therefore proving
to the French people

37:09.595 --> 37:11.296
that the Protestants
have the best interests

37:11.330 --> 37:12.364
of the king at heart.

37:12.397 --> 37:14.866
Sounds risky to me.

37:14.900 --> 37:16.635
<i>Well, you could
always go live in Navarre.</i>

37:16.668 --> 37:18.370
Oh, God, no.

37:18.403 --> 37:20.238
Though it seems very likely
that Mary

37:20.272 --> 37:22.274
and the Holy Roman emperor
will set their sights

37:22.307 --> 37:23.976
on the Protestant kingdom
before long.

37:25.277 --> 37:27.613
Father, what do you think?

37:28.747 --> 37:30.816
Montmorency,

37:30.849 --> 37:33.318
if my sons separate the king
from his wife,

37:33.352 --> 37:34.453
will his eyes be opened?

37:35.854 --> 37:37.789
<i>Frankly, I'm not sure.</i>

37:37.823 --> 37:40.525
I don't believe in him
the way his mother does,

37:40.559 --> 37:42.794
but it might be
your only chance.

37:44.863 --> 37:46.598
All right.

37:47.432 --> 37:49.601
It's bold. It's risky.

37:49.635 --> 37:52.371
From one point of view,
it's profoundly stupid.

37:52.904 --> 37:55.907
From another... inspired.

37:57.576 --> 37:59.578
Because the people are angry.

38:00.278 --> 38:01.780
<i>And if we manage
to pull this off,</i>

38:01.813 --> 38:05.384
we could win their hearts
and minds and perhaps...

38:05.417 --> 38:07.519
come out on top after all.

38:09.287 --> 38:11.323
<i>I like it.</i>

38:11.356 --> 38:13.892
And if it doesn't work,
I'm fucking converting back.

38:15.293 --> 38:17.396
So how--

38:17.429 --> 38:19.398
how does one kidnap a king?

38:21.066 --> 38:22.834
In a few days' time,

38:22.868 --> 38:24.703
the king will travel
with a limited escort

38:24.736 --> 38:27.506
through the forest
near Chambord.

38:27.539 --> 38:30.776
During the journey,
his carriage will be exposed.

38:30.809 --> 38:32.711
How do you know that?

38:32.744 --> 38:35.347
Because I will make it so.

38:37.082 --> 38:39.351
It has come to my attention

38:39.384 --> 38:40.652
that we have not rooted out

38:40.686 --> 38:42.020
all of the Protestants
in France.

38:43.055 --> 38:45.357
There is, in fact,
a secret cell

38:45.390 --> 38:46.758
practicing the heathen faith

38:46.792 --> 38:49.828
not far
from where we sit right now.

38:49.861 --> 38:52.764
Its members may even
include certain...

38:52.798 --> 38:55.734
<i>high-ranking court officials.</i>

38:55.767 --> 38:58.036
<i>The location
of this secret cell</i>

38:58.070 --> 38:59.571
<i>has been delivered to me</i>

38:59.604 --> 39:00.939
<i>through a trusted source.</i>

39:02.708 --> 39:04.776
We must punish these traitors
at once.

39:04.810 --> 39:05.911
Mary, I must caution you--

39:05.944 --> 39:07.946
Queen Mary, Uncle,

39:07.979 --> 39:10.048
or Your Majesty, if you prefer.

39:10.082 --> 39:11.750
Your Majesty,

39:11.783 --> 39:13.485
too much blood's
been spilled already.

39:13.518 --> 39:15.520
It's possible
to push the people too far.

39:15.554 --> 39:18.457
They've seen their countrymen
hanging from trees.

39:18.490 --> 39:20.625
Now, it's one thing
to arrest wealthy Protestants

39:20.659 --> 39:23.662
and another to continually
attack the peasantry.

39:23.695 --> 39:25.063
I think our point
has been made.

39:25.097 --> 39:26.932
Well, I'm not interested
in making a point.

39:26.965 --> 39:29.901
I'm interested in ridding
France of every last infidel,

39:29.935 --> 39:31.436
no matter where I find them,

39:31.470 --> 39:33.472
because the future of Europe
depends on it.

39:36.908 --> 39:41.480
The people will not question
the policy...

39:41.513 --> 39:45.550
if they know the king himself
is firmly behind it.

39:45.584 --> 39:47.052
Yes.

39:47.085 --> 39:48.820
Well said.

39:48.854 --> 39:51.156
I did not expect your support.

39:51.389 --> 39:53.592
But we are glad for it.

39:53.625 --> 39:55.127
Are we not, my king?

39:55.160 --> 39:56.161
Hm?

39:56.394 --> 39:57.863
- Yes.
- Indeed.

39:59.765 --> 40:04.436
We must find a way
to demonstrate

40:04.469 --> 40:07.139
the king's commitment
to the new policy.

40:08.540 --> 40:10.108
All right, then.
Here's what we'll do.

40:10.142 --> 40:11.710
Me and my brother
will go and visit

40:11.743 --> 40:13.445
this secret sect ourselves.

40:13.478 --> 40:14.579
We will see to it.

40:14.613 --> 40:16.414
No.

40:16.448 --> 40:18.016
No. The king should lead us

40:18.049 --> 40:19.518
and confront the infidels himself,

40:19.551 --> 40:21.453
because that sends a message--
a clear message.

40:21.486 --> 40:23.455
That's right,
but the problem is--

40:23.488 --> 40:24.656
I'm not sure the king
is up to it.

40:24.689 --> 40:25.657
Exactly.

40:27.592 --> 40:29.461
Do not doubt his resolve.

40:29.494 --> 40:32.430
I want the people to know
where I stand on this issue.

40:32.464 --> 40:33.198
And they do.

40:35.700 --> 40:37.736
I-it's true, my breathing
sometimes gives me difficulty,

40:37.769 --> 40:38.737
but I am not feeble.

40:38.770 --> 40:40.105
Of course, Your Majesty.

40:40.138 --> 40:42.541
But this is a very,
very dangerous situation.

40:42.574 --> 40:44.476
With all due respect,
the king is sick.

40:44.509 --> 40:45.577
No. The king is fine.

40:45.610 --> 40:46.878
He--

40:46.912 --> 40:49.981
Francis, it's all right, hm?

40:50.015 --> 40:51.783
It's all right. Yeah?

40:53.151 --> 40:54.586
Mm?

40:54.619 --> 40:55.620
<i>Yeah?</i>

40:56.988 --> 40:58.123
You're all right.

40:58.156 --> 40:59.191
I am well.

40:59.224 --> 41:01.726
He is well.

41:01.760 --> 41:03.595
You know,
perhaps it is your resolve

41:03.628 --> 41:05.230
that should be questioned, hm?

41:05.463 --> 41:08.099
It has been said
that even the Catholic Church

41:08.133 --> 41:10.502
is not free of heretics,
and I warn you,

41:10.535 --> 41:11.837
I will leave no stone unturned.

41:11.870 --> 41:14.606
You are either with us,
or you are against us.

41:19.077 --> 41:20.045
We are with you.

41:26.017 --> 41:27.485
Of course.

41:33.692 --> 41:35.727
Come, Francis.

41:43.835 --> 41:45.170
Okay, what are you playing at?

41:45.203 --> 41:47.939
He is in no condition
to do something like this.

41:47.973 --> 41:49.140
<i>True.</i>

41:50.008 --> 41:52.177
But he has God on his side.

42:07.225 --> 42:09.194
<i>You better know
what you're doing.</i>

42:09.227 --> 42:11.029
'Cause our niece
is out of fucking control,

42:11.062 --> 42:13.164
- if you hadn't noticed.
- Just leave it to me.

42:13.198 --> 42:15.133
I'll manage it.

42:15.166 --> 42:17.602
That's what I'm worried about.

42:17.636 --> 42:19.638
Another one
puffed up by Mother...

42:19.671 --> 42:21.673
and now the Holy Roman emperor.

42:23.208 --> 42:25.744
Mary thinks she's
Joan of fucking Arc.

43:01.646 --> 43:02.981
Francis...

43:04.883 --> 43:06.851
...I must ask you
to reconsider your alliance

43:06.885 --> 43:08.320
with the Holy Roman emperor.

43:08.353 --> 43:10.255
And why would he do that?

43:10.288 --> 43:11.957
Hm?

43:11.990 --> 43:13.758
We've been over this.

43:13.792 --> 43:15.627
Francis, please.

43:15.660 --> 43:17.062
I must ask you to reconsider

43:17.095 --> 43:18.763
before we reach
our destination.

43:18.797 --> 43:21.299
Or what happens
at our destination, Mother?

43:21.333 --> 43:22.334
I just don't want
to see anything

43:22.367 --> 43:23.835
happen to you, that's all.

43:23.868 --> 43:25.003
Is that a threat?

43:25.036 --> 43:26.137
Of course not.

43:37.882 --> 43:40.085
You doubt my ability to lead,
don't you?

43:40.118 --> 43:42.020
<i>You have never believed in me
the way Father did</i>

43:42.053 --> 43:43.655
or the way Mary does.

43:43.688 --> 43:45.724
She has always
been there for me.

43:45.757 --> 43:47.659
We can discuss
all of that later,

43:47.692 --> 43:48.927
if you will only
listen to me now.

44:06.111 --> 44:07.345
No wonder father loved Diane.

44:07.379 --> 44:09.047
<i>You could never give him
the love he needed.</i>

44:09.080 --> 44:11.416
You were cold.
I have felt it all my life.

44:11.649 --> 44:14.152
Possessed of the black heart,
just as they say.

44:14.185 --> 44:15.153
You know,
I've even wondered if it's

44:15.186 --> 44:16.254
the blackness in your heart

44:16.287 --> 44:18.056
that caused me
to be born so sickly,

44:18.089 --> 44:21.092
<i>if that's the real reason they
call you the Serpent Queen.</i>

44:25.230 --> 44:27.065
Francis. It's all right.

44:27.098 --> 44:28.900
Help, help, help. Please.

44:28.933 --> 44:30.101
<i>Please, please, help.</i>

44:30.135 --> 44:32.771
Please. Please. Francis.

44:39.978 --> 44:43.381
Indirectly or not, I believe
Catherine was responsible

44:43.415 --> 44:47.285
<i>for what happened
to my husband, the king.</i>

44:50.288 --> 44:52.957
Well, now you know
why you must choose my side.

44:58.463 --> 45:00.832
Thank you for opening my eyes.

45:06.871 --> 45:09.741
I feel my soul cleansed.

45:13.378 --> 45:17.248
I wrote to my cousin in England
asking for help.

45:17.282 --> 45:18.883
If there's one thing
that can unite us,

45:18.917 --> 45:21.786
it is our hatred
of that common queen.

45:23.755 --> 45:24.989
I believe Catherine

45:25.023 --> 45:28.026
has intercepted
her letter in return.

45:29.294 --> 45:31.262
I need it back.

45:31.296 --> 45:32.997
<i>You can find it.</i>

45:35.433 --> 45:37.102
Can I count on you?

45:37.869 --> 45:39.337
It would be my honor

45:39.370 --> 45:42.307
to help you rid France
of the Serpent Queen.

45:42.340 --> 45:43.875
Good.

46:11.536 --> 46:15.140
<i>Find him,
and bring him to me.</i>

46:15.173 --> 46:17.509
Move, posthaste.

46:17.542 --> 46:19.511
Yes, Your Majesty.

46:24.249 --> 46:26.251
I didn't hear you come in.

46:28.353 --> 46:30.355
I came as soon as I could.

46:32.023 --> 46:34.025
Queen Mary let you go.

46:35.326 --> 46:36.294
Why?

46:37.128 --> 46:39.797
I told her a pack of lies
about you.

46:39.831 --> 46:40.965
Now she trusts me.

46:43.568 --> 46:46.371
She even gave me this dress.

46:46.404 --> 46:48.406
I'm not surprised.

46:50.041 --> 46:52.343
You're a clever girl.

46:55.480 --> 46:57.815
Are you angry with me?

46:57.849 --> 47:00.018
Of course not.

47:00.051 --> 47:01.352
You are my friend.

47:01.386 --> 47:03.354
Indeed.

47:03.388 --> 47:06.491
And you have learned
a valuable lesson,

47:06.524 --> 47:09.327
that a queen never lacks
a legitimate reason

47:09.360 --> 47:10.595
to break a promise.

47:17.969 --> 47:20.405
Shall I prepare you a bath?

47:20.438 --> 47:22.840
How thoughtful.

47:31.349 --> 47:33.451
<i>♪ You must leave now ♪</i>

47:33.484 --> 47:35.353
<i>♪ Take what you need ♪</i>

47:35.386 --> 47:39.490
<i>♪ You think will last ♪</i>

47:39.524 --> 47:42.961
<i>♪ But whatever you wish
To keep ♪</i>

47:42.994 --> 47:47.198
<i>♪ You'd better grab it fast ♪</i>

47:48.900 --> 47:52.403
<i>♪ Yonder stands your orphan ♪</i>

47:52.437 --> 47:55.273
<i>♪ With his gun ♪</i>

47:57.308 --> 48:01.112
<i>♪ Crying like a fire ♪</i>

48:01.145 --> 48:04.515
<i>♪ In the sun ♪</i>

48:06.017 --> 48:08.119
<i>♪ Look out ♪</i>

48:08.152 --> 48:12.957
<i>♪ The saints
are coming through ♪</i>

48:14.292 --> 48:18.129
<i>♪ And it's all over now ♪</i>

48:18.162 --> 48:21.032
<i>♪ Baby blue ♪</i>

48:22.934 --> 48:27.005
<i>♪ And it's all over now ♪</i>

